  "rationale": "The FAQ section is architected with a 1fr:2fr grid layout to optimize focus on the vertical FAQ list while maintaining a clean, sidebar-style header. The accordion structure uses a nested 'faq_question-wrapper' and 'faq_answer-wrapper' to facilitate Webflow native interactions (Ix2) for expanding/collapsing. Each 'faq_item' follows a consistent 6-layer Client-First hierarchy, with spacing (2rem padding) and borders defined in 'rem' to ensure fluid responsiveness. Plus/Close icons are housed in a fixed 1rem wrapper to maintain visual balance across all screen sizes. All naming conventions strictly adhere to Finsweet standards (e.g., section_faq, faq_component, faq_item)."
